WEBVTT

00:14:29.200 --> 00:14:31.080
to increase their fonio production.

00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:35.736
Hunger levels are higher
in sub-Saharan Africa

00:14:35.760 --> 00:14:38.200
than any other place in the world.

00:14:39.520 --> 00:14:42.936
The Sahel population is set to grow

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:47.520
from 135 million to 340 million people.

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:52.936
However, in that drought-
and famine-prone region,

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:54.600
fonio grows freely.

00:14:56.360 --> 00:14:59.160
This tiny grain may provide big answers,

00:14:59.960 --> 00:15:02.416
reasserting its Dogon name,